{"tid":1821024,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"又到星期日活動 提提大家 唔好捉鬼","createTime":"2020-01-12T02:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T06:01:59.000Z","uid":24814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0af29fdf7da7eaae8268c921e8c90c7337288b9","tid":1821024,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"你喺網上講乜都得 手足唔介意做完之後賴敵方<br />\n但千祈唔得喺戰場作戰期間捉鬼<br />\n捉錯鬼熱普城、白兵、健吾呢啲人渣就會借題發揮<br />\n公開妖言惑眾搞死心散水 又要嘥時間同佢哋打輿論戰<br />\n捉啱鬼重死 真鬼係有武器 佢殺咗你都重得<br />\n有好多單捉啱都係 結果就係佢哋發爛開槍<br />\n如果你真係覺得有問題嘅人 自己圍內小心啲就得<br />\n<br />\n佢裝修講聲多謝<br />\n不捉鬼但要提防鬼 set好結界同小心可疑車輛<br />\nShare畀每個會出來嘅人"},{"pid":"67063bd393dcfa428a55a1d1c98157f983ca1cd3","tid":1821024,"uid":122201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xp75Hte.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxp75Hte.jpg&h=b7d926a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e60a43ec5ff27f3d5daa356cb4fd924ab3969cb","tid":1821024,"uid":325023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"不捉鬼"},{"pid":"94904bf2656837923bad10d96760b09d6ff13a86","tid":1821024,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">美國議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=6f0012c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</